text: Axel Jöhncke (16 January 1878 - 29 September 1953) was a Swedish fencer. He competed in the individual foil and team sabre events at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1878 births Category:1953 deaths Category:Swedish male fencers Category:Swedish foil fencers Category:Swedish sabre fencers Category:Olympic fencers of Sweden Category:Fencers at the 1912 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Copenhagen
